      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Before promoting any change to production traffic, verify each item:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "text"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "LLMOps Pre-Deployment Checklist\n================================\n\nPROMPT / MODEL\n[ ] Prompt version committed and tagged in git\n[ ] Model pin confirmed (exact version string, not \"latest\")\n[ ] Eval golden set pass rate >= threshold for this prompt \u00d7 model combination\n[ ] Human review completed (if required by change policy)\n[ ] Cost estimate reviewed: monthly increase < 20% vs baseline\n\nINFRASTRUCTURE\n[ ] Config store updated (model pin, prompt version, canary %)\n[ ] Guardrails tested on adversarial inputs\n[ ] Rate limits set for expected peak traffic\n[ ] Health check endpoint returning 200\n\nOBSERVABILITY\n[ ] Tracing confirmed: request_id, model version, prompt version in every log\n[ ] Latency alert thresholds set (TTFT > 3s, E2E > 30s)\n[ ] Quality alert threshold set (7-day rolling mean < baseline - 0.05)\n[ ] Cost alert: daily token spend > 120% of baseline\n\nROLLBACK\n[ ] Previous model pin available in config store\n[ ] Previous prompt version tagged in git\n[ ] Rollback procedure documented and tested in staging\n[ ] On-call engineer briefed\n\nCANARY (if applicable)\n[ ] Canary % confirmed (start at \u2264 5%)\n[ ] Canary monitoring dashboard live\n[ ] Promotion / abort criteria defined (e.g., promote after 48h if metrics healthy)\n"
          }
        ]
      },
